{"tid":2171777,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"319人疑因公染疫 團體促列職業病","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T07:37:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54c2bc0935109775d00486f8e346374fd1972717","tid":2171777,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/6GXCVKNYIBDEDMVBQJBD7HRVQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F6GXCVKNYIBDEDMVBQJBD7HRVQY%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzst4mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=0619c8f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2F6GXCVKNYIBDEDMVBQJBD7HRVQY%2F&h=70722955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/6GXCVKNYIBDEDMVBQJBD7HRVQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n319人疑因公染疫 團體促列職業病<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2UuFjxktBFmd_1BpE-RBraQpqzA=/1282x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IVYDE4OK2RAMPLBET5EKC3JLFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2UuFjxktBFmd_1BpE-RBraQpqzA%3D%2F1282x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIVYDE4OK2RAMPLBET5EKC3JLFE.jpg&h=15c85d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多個工會昨要求政府將武漢肺炎列入職業病，保障打工仔權益。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情反覆，各行各業均有從業員染疫，根據工業傷亡權益會最新統計，由1月23日至本月20日，本港最少有319宗懷疑因公感染武漢肺炎個案，多個工會要求政府盡快將武漢肺炎列入職業病，保障打工仔權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅七僱主承認責任<br />\n<br />\n多個勞工團體召開記者會，要求勞工及福利局將武肺納入《僱員補償條例》指定職業病範圍。據工業傷亡權益會統計，由1月23日至7月22日至少165宗懷疑因公染疫個案，至本月20。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n惟勞工處截至上月22日，僅跟進86宗懷疑因公染疫個案，當中57宗由僱主主動呈報，承認責任的僱主只有七位。<br />\n<br />\n工權會總幹事蕭倩文認為，數字反映因公染疫員工缺乏保障，僱主更毋須承。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟總幹事蒙兆達指，工會已多次提出盡快將武漢肺炎列入職業病，但港府置。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c526f476f7a4bb8eca75a659ffa896663e17ba48","tid":2171777,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uz80KHlwcAXqBMWD9zkMIQwuQcg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OYQ3UYMZRV7VMLDHMLZNZKQFFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUz80KHlwcAXqBMWD9zkMIQwuQcg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOYQ3UYMZRV7VMLDHMLZNZKQFFM.jpg&h=e7c2c935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身都唔預你返 點會列入職業病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}